{% set name = "fixtures" %}
{% set version = "3.0.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.{{ bundle }}
  {{ hash }}: {{ hash_val }}

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed --no-cache-dir -vvv"

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - pip
    - pbr >=0.11

  run:
    - python
    - extras
    - pbr >=0.11
    - six
    - testtools >=0.9.22

test:
  imports:
    - fixtures
    - fixtures.callmany
    - fixtures.fixture
    - fixtures.testcase

about:
